thread.title: Austin on edge after deadly package bombings

title: Austin on edge after deadly package bombings
text:
Austin on edge after deadly package bombings   02:11 
Police have received more than 150 calls about suspicious packages after three parcel bombs left outside homes in Austin, Texas, exploded this month in related attacks that killed two people and injured two others, officials said on Tuesday.
